arts.ttl: Freiburg in Champions League territory after win over ten-man Wolfsburg
arts.sum: SC Freiburg clinched a massive win away from home in a hard-fought game in Wolfsburg.

arts.ttl: Freiburg hold on against 10-man Wolfsburg in Champions League hunt
arts.sum: Max Rosenfelder scored his first Bundesliga goal as Freiburg secured a 1-0 win against 10-man Wolfsburg, strengthening their push for European football next season. However, the game's complexion changed dramatically in the 26th minute when Wolfsburg captain Maximilian Arnold received a straight red card for a reckless challenge on Junior Adamu .

arts.ttl: VfL Wolfsburg vs. SC Freiburg preview: Fifth-place Freiburg look to keep European spot
arts.sum: VfL Wolfsburg (10-9-11, 12th), with a very minimal chance of qualifying for Europe, faces SC Freiburg (14-6-10, 5th), who are heavily involved in European competition with a few teams chasing behind them.
